<CATEGORY> entertainment </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Witherspoon Weds Ryan Phillippe </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Actress Reese Witherspoon and actor Ryan  
Phillippe exchanged nuptials this weekend at a ceremony in South 
Carolina, their publicists said. 
</P>
<P>
	The public relations firm Baker Winokur Ryder said Monday the  
two were married Saturday in Charleston. 
</P>
<P>
	Witherspoon, star of ``Pleasantville'' and ``Election'' is  
pregnant with Phillippe's child. The two co-starred in ``Cruel 
Intentions.'' 
</P>
<P>
	Phillippe's other film credits include ``I Know What You Did  
Last Summer'' and ``54.'' 
  	   	
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
