<HEADLINE> Broncos Sign Shiver to Roster </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	DENVER (AP) -- Clay Shiver, who started 25 games at center for  
Dallas the last two years, signed a contract with the Denver 
Broncos on Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
	The club released no details of the contract.  
</P>
