</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Just before 3 p.m. EDT, the Dow industrials were  
down 137.72 to 10,771.66. Declining issues on the New York Stock 
Exchange led advancers 1,609-1,268. The Nasdaq was down 27.79 to 
2,496.42. 

</P>
