</P>
<P>
	ROME (AP) -- Italian soccer star Christian Vieri is set to be  
sold from Lazio to Internazionale of Milan for $43 million, a 
record deal for the sport. Vieri would be paired up front in Milan 
with Ronaldo, the two-time FIFA World Player of the Year. Ronaldo 
went to Inter for a then-record $28 million two years ago. 

</P>
<P>
	AP NewsBrief by VINCENT CINISOMO  

  	   	
