 *Johns Manville Corp. rose 3/4 to 14    	
</P>
<P>
	Johns Manville will repurchase about $166.8 million common  
shares from its majority shareholder, Manville Personal Injury 
Settlement Trust, and will also prepay its $33.2 million debt to 
the trust. 

</P>
<P>
                              *NASDAQ   	

</P>
<P>
 *Inprise Corp. rose 1 1/8 to 5 1/8    	
</P>
<P>
	Microsoft Corp. will pay $100 million for the right to use  
Inprise's technology and to settle long-standing patent issues. 
Microsoft will also pay $25 million for 10 percent of Inprise's 
preferred shares. Inprise makes software-development tools. 

</P>
<P>
 *drkoop.com Inc., priced at 9, closed at 16 7/16    	
</P>
