 *American Mobile Satellite Corp. rose 3 7/16 to 20 3/16    	
</P>
<P>
	Southeastern Freight Lines Inc. will use American Mobile's  
satellite messaging technology in its fleet. American Mobile will 
equip more than 2,000 trucks within the next 18 months. 

</P>
<P>
 *Select Comfort Corp. fell 5 11/16 to 7 7/16    	
</P>
<P>
	The maker of air beds may report a loss for the second quarter  
of 1999 and expects earnings for the period to be significantly 
below analysts' consensus estimates of 15 cents per share. 

